rows.label: qst006601_msg0001
rows.name:
I haven't eaten a proper
meal in four days!

rows.label: qst006601_msg0002
rows.name:
You could spare some for a poor
soul like me, couldn't you?!

rows.label: qst006601_msg0004
rows.name:
We worked hard to get
these rations too!

rows.label: qst006601_msg0005
rows.name: We can't just hand them over!

rows.label: qst006601_msg0006
rows.name:
What did you say?! In
that case, by force...!

rows.label: qst006601_msg0007
rows.name:
Trying to raise your hand to
a woman? You're the worst!

rows.label: qst006601_msg0009
rows.name:
You're bothering them. If you leave
quietly, we won't do anything.

rows.label: qst006601_msg0010
rows.name:
What do you know about me?! Don't
talk like you know everything!

rows.label: qst006601_msg0011
rows.name:
You two step back a bit. This
will be over in a second.
